        <p>
            EWS is Banking application to assess wether the customer will failure to repay a debt or is a superior customer.
            In this apps has approval flow, reporting, tracking, and tracing.
        </p><br />
        <div class="row grid-items border-line-v">
            <div class="col col-d-3 col-t-3 col-m-12 grid-item photo border-line-h"
                 style="border-top: 1px solid #6c757d !important; border-right: 1px solid #ffce7a !important;">
                <b>Platform</b>
                <ul class="list-style" style="color:black !important">
                    <li>Web</li>
                </ul><br />
            </div>
            <div class="col col-d-3 col-t-3 col-m-12 grid-item photo border-line-h"
                 style="border-top: 1px solid #6c757d !important; border-right: 1px solid #ffce7a !important">
                <b>My Role</b>
                <ul class="list-style" style="color:black !important">
                    <li>Full Stack Developer</li>
                </ul><br />
            </div>
            <div class="col col-d-3 col-t-3 col-m-12 grid-item photo border-line-h"
                 style="border-top: 1px solid #6c757d !important">
                <b>Tech Stack</b>
                <ul class="list-style" style="color:black !important">
                    <li>.Net Core MVC</li>
                    <li>SQL Server</li>
                    <li>IIS Web Server</li>
                </ul>
